WEBVTT

00:16.000 --> 00:19.500
如果我知道 我为政府做的都是下流工作
If I'd known how this was gonna turn out,I'd have gotten some crap job with the feds

00:19.570 --> 00:21.100
再说 我就用枪把
Keep talking like that,I'm gonna put a bullet

00:21.170 --> 00:22.300
你的头打爆
In your head

00:22.370 --> 00:23.600
我知道
We gotta go

00:23.670 --> 00:25.040
有麻烦 是吗?
You're in trouble, aren't you?

00:25.100 --> 00:26.740
维罗妮卡·多诺万?
Veronica Donovan?

00:26.800 --> 00:28.340
你...你是?
Who is this?

00:28.400 --> 00:29.600
我有些可以
I have information

00:29.670 --> 00:31.300
让林肯·布伦斯免除死罪的证据
That will lead to the exoneration of Lincoln Burrows

00:31.370 --> 00:32.640
我必须要检查里面的情况
I gotta check the status in there.

00:32.700 --> 00:34.170
当然可以
It's all good

00:34.240 --> 00:36.070
那么你不会介意我查个清楚吧
Then you won't mind me checking it out.

00:38.770 --> 00:39.840
快把他拉起来!
Get off of him!

00:39.900 --> 00:40.900
把他带走!!!
Get off

00:40.970 --> 00:42.240
快带走...
Get off...

00:42.300 --> 00:43.870
我们今晚离开这
We leave tonight.

00:43.940 --> 00:45.940
迈克尔 我们遇到大问题了
Michael, we got a big problem.

00:46.000 --> 00:48.170
不!
Argh!

00:48.240 --> 00:50.100
不!
Argh!

00:53.270 --> 00:54.440
退出
Back out.

00:54.500 --> 00:55.740
逃离行动?
Of the escape?

00:55.800 --> 00:57.370
要么就死
Or die

01:03.900 --> 01:05.270
约翰 挺住!
Stay with me, John

01:05.340 --> 01:06.740
我要你挺住!
I need you to stay with me.Breathe

01:06.800 --> 01:08.240
我们一起深呼吸...
Keep breathing

01:08.300 --> 01:09.240
一切都会好的
You're gonna be OK

01:09.300 --> 01:10.340
只要你继续呼吸
Keep breathing

01:14.940 --> 01:15.900
约翰 挺住
Stay with me, John

01:15.970 --> 01:16.900
约翰 加油
You stay with me, John

01:16.970 --> 01:17.740
挺住
You stay with me

01:17.800 --> 01:19.700
挺住
Stay with me

01:19.770 --> 01:21.100
为了我 继续呼吸 听到吗?
All right? Can you do that? Keep breathing

01:21.170 --> 01:22.140
为了我 继续呼吸 听到吗?
You gonna be OK. Stay with me

01:22.200 --> 01:23.900
挺住
Stay with me

01:23.970 --> 01:25.940
就在那里 就在...
Almost there.Almost there.

01:39.870 --> 01:41.100
挺住!
...be OK

01:45.670 --> 01:47.240
他失血过多
He's lost a lot of blood

01:47.300 --> 01:48.340
他这样太危险了
He's hypovolemic

01:48.400 --> 01:49.400
他是什么血型?
What's his blood type?

01:49.470 --> 01:50.400
A型
A neg!

01:50.470 --> 01:52.070
他的血压太低
His blood pressure's too low

01:52.140 --> 01:54.240
他太绝望才这样
He's definitely hypovolemic

01:54.300 --> 01:55.300
我们把他送到芝加哥
We gotta get him to Chicago

01:55.370 --> 01:56.670
要飞大约20分钟
Chicago's a 20-minute flight.

02:01.040 --> 02:02.670
医生 我们得出发了
We gotta go, Doc.

02:22.170 --> 02:24.870
现在只有六个人了
And then there were six.

02:27.100 --> 02:28.000
据我所知...
Far as I know

02:28.070 --> 02:30.270
只有5个
There's five

02:34.600 --> 02:37.000
看你以后敢不敢再靠我那么近!
Don't you ever step up to me like that again.

02:38.100 --> 02:39.470
现在谁是老大 啊?
Who's the tough guy now, huh?

02:52.870 --> 02:53.800
狱长?
Warden?

02:53.870 --> 02:55.970
我兄弟在哪?
Where's my brother?

02:56.040 --> 02:58.240
孩子 他现在有麻烦了
He's in a lot of trouble, son.

02:58.300 --> 02:59.840
你得让我去看他
You have to let me see him.

02:59.900 --> 03:02.770
我无法满足你这个请求
That's not a request.I can grant at the moment.

03:02.840 --> 03:04.340
拜托...
Please

03:06.670 --> 03:08.870
我们要关他36小时 一直到他死刑的那个时候
We're 36hours away from his execution

03:08.940 --> 03:11.640
他现在非常暴躁
He panicked.He got violent

03:11.700 --> 03:13.940
因为这样 他剩下的时间将待在狐狸河
For the rest of his time at Fox River

03:14.000 --> 03:15.900
我们给他严格的看守
We're gonna keep him in ad seg,

03:15.970 --> 03:17.370
为了他的安全 也为别人的安全
For his safety and everybody else's.

03:17.440 --> 03:18.700
但我是他的弟弟
I'm his brother.

03:18.770 --> 03:20.700
我应当可以去看他 那是我的权利
I deserve to see him. It's my right.

03:20.770 --> 03:25.540
直到明天你才有权利看到他
It's not your right to see him...until tomorrow...

03:25.600 --> 03:26.600
在他的死刑上
At his execution

03:30.870 --> 03:32.540
孩子 对不起
I'm sorry, son

04:11.900 --> 04:16.530
他的名字叫约翰·阿布鲁奇 A-B-R-U-Z-Z...
The name is John Abruzzi.A-b-r-u-z-z...

04:17.600 --> 04:20.730
我才不关心什么章程制度
I don't care what protocol is

04:20.800 --> 04:23.200
我就是想知道他现在是好是坏
I just want to know if he's OK

04:23.610 --> 04:24.730
喂? 喂?
Hello? Hello?

04:33.270 --> 04:35.570
医院不愿透露一点他的消息
The hospital won't give out any information.

04:35.580 --> 04:39.370
想知道在那家伙身上发生了什么
Wonder what happened to that boy

04:39.380 --> 04:41.130
就像黑手党的鹰犬
Maybe them Mafia chickens

04:41.140 --> 04:42.600
终归要回到他老家一样
Came home to roost after all

04:42.610 --> 04:43.900
我们要掌握整件事
We gotta put this on hold

04:43.970 --> 04:46.370
哦 放轻松点 我们不是什么都掌握不了
Oh, easy, fish. We're not putting nothing on hold

04:46.380 --> 04:47.130
我认为你没在听我的
I don't think you heard me

04:47.140 --> 04:49.320
直到我把我兄弟从那牢房里弄出来
Until I get my brother out at that home

04:49.330 --> 04:50.130
谁也别想这该死的事
No one's doing a damn thing

04:50.140 --> 04:52.600
我很抱歉 但是他已经回不来了
For god bless sake, but the man is gone

04:52.610 --> 04:53.800
进了那个禁闭室
You go to the tombs

04:53.810 --> 04:55.370
那你就出不来了
You don't get out

04:55.430 --> 04:56.800
直到他们把你绑到电椅上
Not until they strap you up

04:56.870 --> 04:59.970
如果你认为我会丢下我兄弟不管
If you think I'll leave my brother behind

05:00.030 --> 05:01.730
那你就真的太低估我了
You have massively underestimated me

05:01.800 --> 05:03.070
-真的吗?  -真的
-Really?  -Really

05:03.130 --> 05:04.270
耶 但那可不包括在我的行程之内
That ain't my flight

05:05.830 --> 05:07.730
我可以很漂亮的穿过那个牢房 无论有没有你
I'm through that hole, pretty,with or without you

05:07.800 --> 05:09.770
下一次就是在我自由活动的时候
Next time I'm on PI

05:09.830 --> 05:10.700
我们别再这样争论下去了
We're not having this debate

05:10.770 --> 05:11.670
我们不争论?
We're not having this debate?

05:11.730 --> 05:12.870
我们别再这样争论下去了
We're not having this debate

05:12.930 --> 05:14.300
为什么我们不去把那地板砸开
We oughta open the floor

05:14.370 --> 05:15.330
给每一个人?
To everyone else

05:15.400 --> 05:16.970
看看他们都在说什么
See what they all say?

05:17.030 --> 05:18.830
宝贝 你懂吗?
We got a clear shot

05:18.900 --> 05:20.970
我们再不用那个洞
Every day we don't use that hole is another day

05:21.030 --> 05:22.600
迟早会被条子发现的
The screws can find it

05:22.670 --> 05:23.770
这个方法还没结束
The way is not finished

05:23.830 --> 05:24.870
我们都很清楚
We're clear to the infirmary

05:24.930 --> 05:28.430
那个医务室 就是我所需要的
That's all we need

05:28.500 --> 05:30.970
穿过那扇窗户
Through that window

05:31.030 --> 05:34.070
越过那铁丝网 越过那墙
Over that wire, over that wall

05:34.130 --> 05:37.730
你们两个是不可能做到的
The two of you will never make it

05:37.800 --> 05:39.430
哦 宝贝 这不止两个人
Oh, fish, it's not just two.

05:43.170 --> 05:46.630
无论怎么样 我们必须要走
If it's now or never, we gotta go

05:46.700 --> 05:48.070
迈克尔 和我们一起走
Go with us.Michael

05:48.130 --> 05:50.430
你已经做了你该做的
You've done everything you could

05:50.500 --> 05:51.470
大家都是成年人 迈克尔
They're grown men, Michael.

05:51.530 --> 05:53.470
大家都会为自己做打算
They can all decide for themselves

05:53.480 --> 05:54.630
你他妈狗娘养的...
You son of a...

05:54.700 --> 05:56.030
喂 住手 后退
Wait a minute!

05:56.100 --> 05:58.370
你们两个人立刻分开
Hey! Who are you separating there?

05:58.430 --> 05:59.470
嘿 老大 没事没事
Hey, it's good, boss

05:59.480 --> 06:00.480
只是在一起玩玩
Just playing around

06:00.490 --> 06:01.470
没事
It's all good

06:05.030 --> 06:07.000
现在你知道了
You know, there are

06:07.070 --> 06:10.490
这有两件每一个人都必须要遵守的事
Two things that everybody needs to give with here

06:10.500 --> 06:14.070
首先 乡巴佬 彻底地学会尊敬
First, hillbilly,you have got to learn some respect

06:14.130 --> 06:16.330
没有他就没有逃走计划
The man here made everything possible

06:19.470 --> 06:20.530
至于你呢 嫩鸡
And you fish?

06:20.600 --> 06:22.400
现在你必须学会它
You're gonna have to get with that

06:22.470 --> 06:23.800
我们今天下午就开工
We are doing this thing this afternoon

06:23.870 --> 06:25.330
在我们开始自由活动之前
As soon as we get on PI

06:27.970 --> 06:31.100
所以你要冒这个险
So you're just gonna make a run for it

06:31.110 --> 06:32.070
在今天中午
In the middle of the day

06:32.130 --> 06:33.470
伙计 你得这样做
Well, you gotta do

06:33.480 --> 06:33.970
否则你还能做什么呢 宝贝?
What you gotta do, huh, baby?

06:35.980 --> 06:38.230
你会把整个事情都搞砸了
You are gonna screw this whole thing up

06:38.900 --> 06:42.200
你不能再为你自己而替大家做决定
That's not for you to decide any more

06:42.270 --> 06:45.000
现在 我们的事已经进入轨道
Now, this train is leaving the station

06:45.070 --> 06:47.130
我劝你最好和我们一起干
And I suggest you get on it

06:47.140 --> 06:50.530
一起干吧 宝贝 我们一起干
Get on the train, fish.Get on the train.

06:50.600 --> 06:54.930
好啊 你知道什么 你们他妈的狗娘养的
Well, you know what, you sons of bitches?

06:55.000 --> 06:56.570
我不会让你们这么做的
I won't let you do it

06:56.630 --> 06:57.570
你想干吗?
What you gonna do?

06:57.630 --> 06:58.500
边告密
Blow the whistle

06:58.570 --> 07:00.400
边离开这鬼地方
On your own escape?

07:04.070 --> 07:05.170
他会回来的
He'll be back

07:36.200 --> 07:37.900
那些家伙
Those guys

07:37.910 --> 07:40.600
他们今晚会在我们之前从那个洞离开这
They go before us tonight,they use that hole

07:40.610 --> 07:42.570
那就完了
It's over

07:42.630 --> 07:45.270
那些警察会把这翻个底朝天
COs will turn this whole place upside down

07:45.330 --> 07:46.330
直到他们发现那洞
Till they find it

07:46.400 --> 07:48.430
好啦...
Well...

07:48.500 --> 07:50.000
听起来 你一直都在想这件事
Sounds like you're thinking about it

07:51.830 --> 07:54.230
如果我说不 那其实是撒谎
I'd be lying if I said I wasn't

07:54.300 --> 07:57.470
我昨天还想从这里逃出去
I want to be out of here yesterday

07:57.530 --> 08:00.100
伙计 我要做爸爸了
I got a kid coming, man

08:03.610 --> 08:06.210
迈克尔 你不可能把他从这里弄出去
Michael, you can't get him out of there.

08:13.670 --> 08:15.040
我可以说吗?
Can I say something?

08:15.110 --> 08:17.140
我知道你并不想听这些
I know you won't want to hear it

08:17.210 --> 08:19.170
但是 呃...
But...

08:19.240 --> 08:21.870
现在他们是非让他上电椅不可了
They're strapping him up either way now

08:21.940 --> 08:23.070
一旦他没了
Once he's gone

08:23.140 --> 08:25.640
你很可能还要在里面再待上5年
You'll be stuck here for another five years.

08:25.710 --> 08:27.510
同样 他们也会根据那个洞查到你
If they trace the hole back to you

08:27.570 --> 08:29.210
他们又将再判你个徒刑
They'll toss another dime.

08:29.270 --> 08:31.670
那可是15年啊 兄弟!
That's 15 years.Papi!

08:36.370 --> 08:37.610
当然 如果我是你
Of course, if I were you

08:37.670 --> 08:40.470
我也不会丢下我兄弟不顾
I wouldn't leave my brother behind either.

08:40.540 --> 08:42.110
不要这要死 不
Not to die like that, no

08:42.170 --> 08:44.970
恩...恩...
Uh-uh

08:45.040 --> 08:47.240
他们对一个男人做的这个世界上最糟的一件事
Worst thing in the world they can do to a man

08:47.310 --> 08:49.370
就是像那样用绳子把他捆在椅子上
Is strap him to a chair like that

09:04.940 --> 09:05.870
我们有事要做了
We're in business

09:05.940 --> 09:06.840
什么意思?
What do you mean?

09:06.910 --> 09:08.110
我刚和我的一个朋友通电话
I just spoke to a friend

09:08.120 --> 09:10.440
他是最高法院的秘书
Who's a clerk at the superior court

09:10.510 --> 09:11.740
我告诉他关于提供情报的人的事
I told him about the informer

09:11.810 --> 09:13.140
你要在8点和他见面
You must meet him at 8o'clock

09:13.210 --> 09:14.770
如果他提供给我们能够缓刑的证据
If he gives any evidence to warrant a stay

09:14.780 --> 09:16.740
我朋友说他会尽力帮助我们
My friend will hear us out

09:16.810 --> 09:18.540
我们还是有希望阻止这一切
We still might be able to stop this

09:18.610 --> 09:19.370
我得去告诉林肯
I gotta tell Lincoln

09:19.440 --> 09:20.770
你要去那所监狱
You go to that prison

09:20.840 --> 09:22.410
你知道 他们总会在你身边
They'll be all over you you know that.

09:22.470 --> 09:24.740
他们总是想让我们疲于奔命
They've kept us on the run entired time.

09:24.810 --> 09:27.240
因为我们把他公之与众 他们就完了
Because if anyone hears from us, we can do them damage

09:27.310 --> 09:31.070
也许 我们在做着完全相反的事
Maybe it's time we do the exact opposite... go big

09:31.140 --> 09:33.070
什么意思 大的?
What do you mean, "big"?

09:33.140 --> 09:34.870
你的意思是找大媒体
You mean media big?

09:34.940 --> 09:36.540
我们证据确凿
We got all the ammo we need

09:36.610 --> 09:38.110
排起来有一公里长谋杀犯
There's a string of murders a mile long

09:38.170 --> 09:40.110
受这件事的牵连 我们要揭露...
Connected to this.We will...

09:40.170 --> 09:42.770
你已经准备好再一次面对媒体了吗? 呃?
Are you ready to show your face again? Huh?

09:42.840 --> 09:44.810
你真的准备好了吗?
Are you ready for that?

09:44.870 --> 09:49.470
事已至此 我们还能做什么其他的呢?
It's the bottom of the ninth.What else are we gonna do?

10:10.410 --> 10:12.340
喂?
Hello?

10:12.410 --> 10:16.210
喂 是爸爸 宝贝女儿
Hey. This is Daddy, baby girl.

10:16.270 --> 10:17.970
爸爸
Daddy!

10:18.040 --> 10:19.670
爸爸打来的电话
Daddy is on the phone.

10:19.740 --> 10:22.140
骆驼怎么样啦?
How are the camels?

10:22.210 --> 10:24.640
噢 好的 骆驼嘛 嗯 ...
Oh, well, the camels...

10:24.710 --> 10:26.440
骆驼都很好
The camels are fine

10:26.510 --> 10:28.470
我什么时候可以看见你?
When do I get to see you?

10:28.540 --> 10:30.770
比我想象的要早
Earlier than I thought

10:30.840 --> 10:33.310
爸爸说他很快就要回来了
Daddy said he's coming home soon

10:33.370 --> 10:35.740
把电话拿给妈妈
Hey, put Mommy on the phone

10:38.510 --> 10:40.710
谢谢你 甜心
Thank you, sweetie

10:40.770 --> 10:43.570
第一军士 本杰明·迈尔斯·富兰克林
First Sergeant Benjamin Miles Franklin

10:43.640 --> 10:44.870
你好吗?
How are you?

10:44.940 --> 10:48.440
呃 宝贝...只是开卡车来打发时间
Oh, baby. Just driving trucks,eating dates

10:48.510 --> 10:50.710
试着不让沙子钻进眼睛
Trying to keep the sand out of my eyes

10:50.770 --> 10:51.810
那天我看了新闻
I saw on the news the other day

10:51.870 --> 10:53.210
在科威特 华氏110度
It was 110 in Kuwait.

10:53.270 --> 10:54.210
你肯定要被晒化了
You must be melting

10:54.270 --> 10:55.210
在那
Over there

10:55.270 --> 10:57.340
你不知道那里有多热
You have no idea

10:57.410 --> 10:59.840
我听说你很快要回来了 是真的吗?
What's this about you coming home?

10:59.910 --> 11:01.970
你是不会让女儿希望落空的 不是吗?
You're not getting your daughter's hopes up?

11:02.040 --> 11:04.240
你坐稳了吗
You sitting down?

11:04.310 --> 11:05.740
那是当然
Sure

11:05.810 --> 11:07.610
你老公这周就能回到家
Your man is coming home this week

11:07.670 --> 11:08.610
这周?
This week?

11:08.670 --> 11:09.810
你说的是真的吗?
What are you talking about?

11:09.870 --> 11:11.210
他们不是说你要
They said

11:11.270 --> 11:12.470
明年才能回来
It'd be another year

11:12.540 --> 11:14.340
嘿 命令已经下来了 宝贝
The orders just came down the pipe.

11:14.410 --> 11:17.310
现在 我可不关心这里的温度是否降下来
And the hell if I care where they came down from.

11:17.370 --> 11:18.640
我所关心的是
All that matters is

11:18.710 --> 11:20.010
我们可以见面了
we will see each other

11:20.070 --> 11:21.840
什么时候回来?什么时候?
When? When is this happening?

11:21.910 --> 11:24.540
星期四 星期五 呃...我还不确定
Thursday, Friday. I'm not sure yet.

11:24.610 --> 11:25.940
噢 我的上帝 
Oh,my God!

11:26.010 --> 11:27.870
要让我去机场接你回来吗?
Do you need me to pick you up from the airport?

11:27.940 --> 11:32.340
噢 不 不 不要 呃...部队会负责到底的
Oh, no. No, no.The army's got that all that arranged

11:32.410 --> 11:34.810
你知道的 你只要在家里等着我就好
You know, you just be waiting for me

11:34.870 --> 11:36.840
好的 你知道我要让把它们全记下来
Well, you know I got that down

11:41.610 --> 11:43.010
拜托 后退点?
Would you back up?

11:45.970 --> 11:48.540
嘿 嘿 呃 你知道的 指挥官只让我多使用
Hey, you know, Comm is only letting me use this linkup

11:48.610 --> 11:51.210
这电话机几分钟 所以 呃...
For a few more minutes

11:51.270 --> 11:52.170
呃 戴里斯在吗?
Is Darius there?

11:52.240 --> 11:53.410
我要和他说话
I need to speak to him

11:53.470 --> 11:56.470
呃 在 在 我去叫他
Yeah, yeah. I'll go get him.

11:56.540 --> 11:58.310
我爱你
I love you

11:58.370 --> 12:01.770
我也爱你
I love you more

12:02.840 --> 12:04.340
哟
Yo

12:05.370 --> 12:07.810
哟 怎么啦 哥们?
Yeah, what's up, money?

12:10.140 --> 12:12.010
你妹妹出去了吗?
Your sister out of the room?

12:13.070 --> 12:14.810
是的
She is now

12:14.870 --> 12:17.610
哥们 那外面到底是什么情形?
So, how is it out there, man?

12:17.670 --> 12:18.610
狐狸河真的就像
Fox River all that

12:18.670 --> 12:19.610
他们所说得那样?
They say it is?

12:19.670 --> 12:21.570
不全是这样
Oh, man, it ain't all that

12:21.640 --> 12:23.170
无论如何 不能太久
Not for long, anyway

12:23.240 --> 12:24.540
你是什么意思?
What you mean by that?

12:24.610 --> 12:26.370
我要你帮我做些事
I need you to do something for me

12:26.440 --> 12:28.070
好 好 当然没问题
Yeah, all right.

12:28.140 --> 12:30.070
你还是开那辆凯迪拉克攀登者吗?
You still drive that Escalader?

12:30.140 --> 12:32.140
迈克尔·杰克逊还是白人吗?
Is Michael Jackson still white?

12:32.210 --> 12:34.540
孩子 你就会开玩笑
Ha-ha, you gotjokes, son

12:34.610 --> 12:37.240
能装多少人?
How many does it hold?

12:40.110 --> 12:42.110
好的
OK

12:43.610 --> 12:45.940
好什么?
OK what?

12:47.610 --> 12:49.610
我们干吧
Let's do it

12:50.610 --> 12:52.710
什么 你的意思是今晚?
What? You mean tonight?

12:52.770 --> 12:54.870
那林肯怎么办?
What about Linc?

12:55.870 --> 12:58.510
我需要一片剃刀刀片
I need a razor blade

12:58.570 --> 12:59.510
迈克尔 一片剃刀刀片
A razor blade

12:59.570 --> 13:00.510
也不能把他从里面弄出来
Ain't gonna get him out

13:00.570 --> 13:03.470
你有还是没有?
Do you have one or not?

13:06.570 --> 13:08.810
兄弟 小心
Careful, brother

14:20.000 --> 14:22.670
引导我去接近水源
Leadeth me beside the still waters

14:22.740 --> 14:24.840
修复我的灵魂
Restoreth my soul

14:24.900 --> 14:27.170
请您引导我走上公正之路
Leadeth me in the path of righteousness for your sake

14:27.240 --> 14:30.500
尽管我走在死亡阴影的山谷中...
Though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death

14:30.570 --> 14:32.000
我不怕恶魔
I will fear no evil

14:32.070 --> 14:34.870
我不怕恶魔 和我一同分享你的艺术
I will fear no evil.For thou art with me

14:34.940 --> 14:38.870
你在我的敌人都在场的时候
In the presence of mine enemies

14:38.880 --> 14:40.040
在我前面准备一张桌子
Thou preparest a table before me

14:40.100 --> 14:45.200
当然 善良与仁慈...
Surely goodness and mercy

14:45.270 --> 14:46.870
将一直伴随我们一生
Shall follow me all the days of my life

14:46.940 --> 14:51.800
我们将永远受主的恩惠
And I will dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

14:51.870 --> 14:53.970
阿门
Amen

14:54.040 --> 14:55.670
阿门
Amen

14:56.800 --> 14:59.870
他能听见我们的祈祷 你知道的 上帝
He does hear our prayers, the Lord...

14:59.940 --> 15:00.790
是的
Yes

15:00.810 --> 15:02.840
关于对林肯的支持
...on behalf of Lincoln

15:04.170 --> 15:08.670
所有那些寻找宽恕的人们都将得到宽恕
All who seek forgiveness will be delivered

15:08.740 --> 15:09.700
是的
Yes.

15:09.770 --> 15:11.770
如果你兄弟接受了主的安排
If your brother accepts the Lord

15:11.780 --> 15:13.970
他将得到永远的自由
He'll be free of this cage forever

15:14.540 --> 15:15.700
是的
Yes

15:17.870 --> 15:21.000
我将一直全程陪伴着他
I'll be available through this whole thing

15:21.010 --> 15:22.470
如果你需要的话
If you need me

15:22.540 --> 15:24.540
尊敬的牧师...
Reverend

15:26.700 --> 15:30.500
尊敬的牧师 你能将这个给我哥哥吗?
Reverend, would you give this to my brother?

15:32.370 --> 15:37.040
这对他意味着很多 他一看就知道是我给他的
It'd mean a lot to him,knowing it came from me

15:38.070 --> 15:40.900
我会转交给他的
I will

15:53.340 --> 15:56.170
那是我妈妈的
That was my mother's

15:56.240 --> 15:59.270
告诉她 这将会使一个人摆脱痛苦
Tell her it's going to save someone a lot of pain

15:59.340 --> 16:02.600
你确定你做这些有用吗?
You sure you know what you're doing?

16:04.840 --> 16:07.870
这得看他的造化了
It's in God's hands now.

16:12.070 --> 16:13.840
感觉好像你一直在给我作善后的事情
You've been the clean-up crew for me

16:13.900 --> 16:15.540
我在这里的这段时间
The whole time I've been in here

16:15.600 --> 16:20.600
脚趾受伤 打伤... 注射胰岛素
Toes, contusions, insulin shots

16:20.670 --> 16:22.270
总得有人做吧
Well, somebody's gotta do it

16:22.340 --> 16:23.870
非常感激
Well, I'm grateful

16:24.940 --> 16:28.200
你还想过... 另一种生活...
You ever think, in another life...

16:28.270 --> 16:30.370
我不会是那样的 女人 迈克尔
I won't be that woman, Michael

16:30.440 --> 16:32.770
我不是要你成为那样
I wasn't asking you to be

16:32.840 --> 16:34.570
但是 有些事
But it is something

16:34.640 --> 16:36.570
我想知道
I wonder about

16:36.640 --> 16:38.900
如果...
What if?

16:41.600 --> 16:46.140
不管怎样 只是想确定你所说的
Anyway, just wanted to make sure it was said

16:46.200 --> 16:49.640
为什么我的感觉就像是要跟你说再见?
Why do I feel like you're saying goodbye to me?

16:49.700 --> 16:52.500
我不知道
I don't know

16:52.570 --> 16:54.000
我想在象这样的地方
I guess in a place like this

16:54.070 --> 16:56.970
你不会知道哪天才是你的最后一天
you never know which day is gonna be your last

16:59.900 --> 17:01.240
莎拉 我这需要你的帮助
Sara, we got a backup out here.

17:01.300 --> 17:02.970
好的
OK

17:03.040 --> 17:04.040
你感觉下
You're set

17:06.740 --> 17:10.270
我 呃...
I...

17:10.340 --> 17:12.340
我对你哥哥的事表示遗憾
I'm sorry about your brother

17:16.170 --> 17:17.340
医生...
Doctor...

17:27.100 --> 17:29.140
谢谢
Thank you

18:19.070 --> 18:21.370
兄弟 时间到了
This is it, brother

18:23.400 --> 18:25.040
嘿
Hey

18:30.900 --> 18:32.640
祝我们好运
Good luck to both of us

18:32.700 --> 18:34.790
监狱工厂的 干活了!
PI! Let's do it!

18:51.200 --> 18:54.040
你有没有弄明白啊?
Came to your senses, did you?

18:56.700 --> 18:58.300
比如 你计算的神奇的方法
What did you figure a magic way

18:58.370 --> 18:59.840
把你兄弟从那里弄出来
to get your brother out of that hole

18:59.900 --> 19:01.340
和进入到警卫室里去
And into the guards' room?

19:01.400 --> 19:04.170
他用不着去那里
He's not gonna be there

19:11.070 --> 19:13.270
麻烦能把灯打开吗?
Could you put the light on?

19:15.370 --> 19:17.670
你好吗?
You OK?

19:19.500 --> 19:20.500
你在想什么 雷夫?
What do you think, Rev?

19:22.700 --> 19:24.330
今天我和你弟弟谈了一次
I spoke with your brother today

19:24.400 --> 19:26.460
他真诚为你做了祈祷
He's been praying for you

19:26.530 --> 19:28.160
他一定非常的绝望
He must be desperate

19:28.230 --> 19:30.830
你呢?
What about you?

19:30.900 --> 19:32.630
你觉得绝望吗?
Are you feeling desperate?

19:32.700 --> 19:36.830
不 只是让某些人绝望而已
No.Just for everyone else

19:36.900 --> 19:39.060
那些你舍弃不顾的那些人
The ones you leave behind

19:40.330 --> 19:43.900
那些我还没说再见的人
The ones I never got to say goodbye to

19:43.960 --> 19:46.160
你知道的 我明天一直陪伴着你...
I can be with you all day tomorrow, you know.

19:46.230 --> 19:47.930
包括那个时候
Right up to the time

19:49.730 --> 19:51.460
谢谢
Thank you

19:51.530 --> 19:55.060
嗯 他要我把这个给你
He wanted me to give this to you

19:56.130 --> 19:58.060
迈克尔
Michael

20:29.760 --> 20:31.360
她回来了
She's back in play

20:31.430 --> 20:33.100
好的 谁和你在一起?
Good. Who's there with you?

20:33.160 --> 20:34.630
唐格
Tangren

20:34.700 --> 20:36.060
哈尔怎么样?
What about Hale?

20:36.130 --> 20:38.760
迈阿密
Nope. MIA.

20:38.830 --> 20:41.130
估计他也会在那里 你是什么意思 迈阿密?
He should be there. What do you mean, MIA?

20:41.200 --> 20:43.730
我想这是一个相当简洁的说法
I think it's a fairly concise term

20:51.730 --> 20:53.330
别接
Don't get it.

20:57.660 --> 20:59.900
-飞机是几点的?  -11:00
-What time's the flight?  -11:00

20:59.960 --> 21:02.160
别对任何人说 我要去 瑞格镇
Don't tell anyone.I gotta head up to Wrigleyville.

21:02.230 --> 21:04.430
我两个小时候回来接你
I'll be back in a couple hours to collect you

21:04.500 --> 21:06.560
现在确定东西都收拾好
Make sure you pack everything

21:06.630 --> 21:09.160
一旦我们出了这扇门 我们就不再会回来
Once we're out that door,we won't come back

21:09.230 --> 21:10.360
你要去干什么?
What are you gonna do?

21:10.430 --> 21:13.160
有一封信要送
There's a letter I gotta deliver.

21:16.260 --> 21:18.260
女士 你要退后点

21:18.330 --> 21:19.230
听我说
Listen

21:19.300 --> 21:20.760
我叫维罗妮卡·多诺万
I'm Veronica Donovan

21:20.830 --> 21:21.830
我是林肯·布伦斯的代表律师
I represent Lincoln Burrows

21:21.900 --> 21:23.100
很好 但现在不是谈这个的时候
Great, this isn't the time for it.

21:23.160 --> 21:24.160
你必须靠边站
You'll have to step aside

21:24.230 --> 21:25.530
呃 对不起 多诺万小姐?
I'm sorry.Miss Donovan?

21:25.600 --> 21:27.260
你是不是说你是林肯·布伦斯的代表律师?
Did you say that you represent Lincoln Burrows?

21:27.330 --> 21:28.960
林肯·布伦斯? 是的
Lincoln Burrows?That's right

21:29.030 --> 21:30.630
安吉拉·维斯特 我是六频道新闻的主管
Angela West. I'm a producer with News Six

22:10.730 --> 22:14.130
派得·派普(德国神话中吹笛带走老鼠的人) 下面怎么进行下去?
So, Mr Pied Piper, what's the play?

22:14.200 --> 22:17.560
我们在做我们一直做的事: 假装工作
We do what we always do pretend to be working

22:17.630 --> 22:22.430
假装良民 直到恰当的时候
Be model citizens...till the time comes

22:22.500 --> 22:23.730
你说几点?
And that'd be?

22:23.800 --> 22:24.960
9点
Nine o'clock

22:25.030 --> 22:26.260
好像忘记了
You seem to be forgetting

22:26.330 --> 22:29.030
工作时间好像是5点结束
That PI shuts down at five o'clock

22:29.100 --> 22:31.730
那么我就得保证这没法按时结束 不是吗?
Well, we have to make sure it doesn't, don't we?

22:44.660 --> 22:45.800
锤子
Hammer

22:51.330 --> 22:53.200
哇 哇 你他妈的在干什么?
Whoa! What the hell are you doing, man?

23:11.400 --> 23:12.830
这里到底发生了什么?
What the hell happened here?

23:12.900 --> 23:14.300
混乱不堪 水管破了
Messed up. Hit a pipe

23:14.360 --> 23:16.660
本应该在我们工作之前就该把水关掉 不是吗?
Should've killed the water Before we started?

23:16.730 --> 23:18.260
应该吗?
Should've?

23:18.330 --> 23:19.860
这可不是件麻烦的事
It's not that big a deal

23:19.930 --> 23:21.600
我们可以在早晨之前修好它
We can fix it in the morning

23:21.660 --> 23:23.260
我可不想
I don't think

23:23.330 --> 23:25.560
石膏那时候就会发霉了
Mould should be a problem before then.

23:25.630 --> 23:26.830
石膏?
Mould?

23:26.900 --> 23:27.560
斯科菲尔德 闭嘴
Scofield.shut up, man

23:27.630 --> 23:28.560
不 你闭嘴
You shut up

23:28.630 --> 23:29.860
你在说什么?
What are you talking about?

23:29.930 --> 23:32.730
得把墙壁和木板都弄干
You get drywall and insulation soaked like this

23:32.800 --> 23:35.260
否则石膏会发霉
You run the risk of stachybotrys mould

23:35.330 --> 23:36.760
老大...
Boss

23:36.830 --> 23:40.360
不太可能的 一千次中也最多就发生一次
that's just, like,one time in a thousand, for real

23:40.430 --> 23:42.300
告诉你
Tell you what

23:42.360 --> 23:44.530
你 还有你们几个
You and all your compa

23:44.600 --> 23:45.930
你在这的同伴
Eros here

23:46.000 --> 23:47.300
别想走出这个门一步
Aren't stepping outside this door

23:47.360 --> 23:48.400
直到这该死的
Until every damn

23:48.460 --> 23:49.800
每一滴水
Molecule of water

23:49.860 --> 23:51.430
都不会从这再流出来
Is out of this place

23:51.500 --> 23:52.700
那可得花上一晚上的功夫
It's gonna take all night

23:52.760 --> 23:56.160
好啊 那你们就干一晚上
Well, then it's gonna take all night.

23:56.230 --> 23:58.930
不要着凉啊
Don't catch a sniffle

24:10.000 --> 24:11.600
你凶
Man

24:18.500 --> 24:20.160
许多事情都要核查清楚
A lot of it checks out

24:20.230 --> 24:21.330
她?
Put her on

24:21.400 --> 24:22.600
多诺万小姐 如果你不介意
Miss Donovan.If you don't mind

24:22.660 --> 24:24.260
我们想让你上镜受采访
We'd like to put you on

24:24.330 --> 24:25.700
没问题 那就是我来这的原因
That's why I'm here

24:25.760 --> 24:27.100
那就好 豪利 在这要
Great.Holly here

24:27.160 --> 24:28.300
问你几个问题
Will be asking the questions

24:28.360 --> 24:30.030
看他的手势 准备好了吗?
Just watch his hand, OK?

24:34.160 --> 24:35.660
晚间新闻 皮特
Night NEWS Peter

24:35.730 --> 24:38.060
在我身边的是维罗妮卡·多诺万 林肯·布伦斯的代理律师
I'm with Veronica Donovan,the lawyer for Lincoln Burrows

24:39.230 --> 24:40.360
你正在为他作最后的努力 是吗?
You're petitioning for a stay, is that right?

24:40.430 --> 24:41.460
是的
Yes

24:41.530 --> 24:42.860
基于什么呢?
On what grounds?

24:42.930 --> 24:44.660
我有充分的理由 我的当事人是被陷害的
On the grounds that my client was framed

24:44.730 --> 24:46.930
把她的细节套出来
Get specifics

24:47.000 --> 24:49.430
维罗妮卡·多诺万 你有什么充分而有力的证据吗?
Veronica Donovan.Do you have any proof?

24:49.500 --> 24:51.760
有一条线索显示: 凶手...
There's a whole string of proof.Murders...

24:51.830 --> 24:53.860
莱提卡·巴里斯 一个 知道真相的目击证人
Leticia Barris.A potential exculpatory witness

24:53.930 --> 24:54.960
莉萨·利克斯
Lisa Rix

24:55.030 --> 24:56.860
林肯的妻子
The mother of Lincoln's child

24:56.930 --> 24:58.330
比斯霍普·迈克莫罗 他
Bishop McMorrow

24:58.400 --> 24:59.760
已经向联邦政府提出重审请求
Who could have petitioned for clemency

24:59.830 --> 25:02.000
你是说有别人杀了他们 而嫁祸别人?
Someone's killing these people off?

25:02.060 --> 25:05.030
我的意思是有人想掩盖事实的真相
I'm saying somebody's trying to hide what happened

25:05.100 --> 25:07.400
特伦斯·斯蒂德曼的事实 真相到底是怎样
The truth about Terrence Steadman

25:07.460 --> 25:09.930
这些只是你得推测 还是有了强而有力
Is this all just speculation, or is there hard evidence

25:10.000 --> 25:11.800
支持你推断的证据?
To substantiate your claims?

25:11.860 --> 25:13.160
我有根据
I have a source

25:13.230 --> 25:14.330
要他的名字
Get a name

25:14.400 --> 25:15.700
你现在的心情是不是非常的复杂?
Could you elaborate?

25:15.760 --> 25:17.600
不是现在这个时候 但是有人现在在监狱里
No.Somebody on the inside

25:17.660 --> 25:21.660
坚持声称他是无辜的 应当被无罪释放
Claims they can exonerate Lincoln,that Terrence Steadman wasn't in the car that night

25:22.400 --> 25:26.060
有人已经说出来了
Someone's been talking

25:35.400 --> 25:38.130
是用直流电吗?
Is there a reason you're on direct current?

25:38.200 --> 25:39.300
怎么了?
Sorry?

25:39.360 --> 25:41.760
你知道 交流电/直流电
You know, AC/DC.

25:41.830 --> 25:45.060
换电流 用直流电
Alternating current, direct current.DC's kinda

25:45.130 --> 25:48.860
直流电比较落后
Yesterday's news for this sort of thing

25:48.930 --> 25:52.600
你可以只用交流电的一半能量就可以处死那个人
You can kill a man with half the energy if you go AC

25:55.730 --> 25:56.830
好的
OK

25:56.900 --> 25:58.430
看看我们干的
Let's see what we got

26:04.330 --> 26:07.360
准备好了吗?
You ready to run one?

26:42.000 --> 26:44.600
警官们 我认为最好把这些灯打开
Sir.I think you better turn these lights on.

26:44.670 --> 26:45.900
小姐 我们不能这么做
Miss.Can't do it

26:45.970 --> 26:47.270
你的当事人正在被关禁闭
Your client's being disciplined

26:47.330 --> 26:50.230
你触犯了我当事人的合法权利
You're violating his Eighth Amendment rights

26:50.300 --> 26:52.230
你要么5秒钟后把灯打开
Either you turn those lights on at next five seconds.

26:52.300 --> 26:55.730
要么你就准备作被告
Or you'll be the first defendant named in a lawsuit

27:17.170 --> 27:18.600
你好吗?
You OK?

27:20.800 --> 27:22.970
我儿子好吗?
LJ?

27:23.030 --> 27:26.000
他很好
He's good

27:27.030 --> 27:29.930
